Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝指導
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球放到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一節什麼課
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}好  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近總愛偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明天開始記得穿胸罩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句話就被打擊成這樣的我還第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來  這也演得太過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出一副世界末日的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底點中了她哪個笑穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前跟大家討論件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於文化祭班級出演的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有什麼點子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提議咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞輕鬆點的吧  輕鬆點的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女僕咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學  請講
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提議反串劇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反串？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女生飾演角色時互換性別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的一齣劇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺很適合更科同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學典禮時穿立領嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來多數表決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\fad(700,0)}（文化祭出演節目  咖啡店  鬼屋  女僕咖啡店  反串劇）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就決定舞台劇了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要寫劇本的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先整理好梗概交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺會很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然決定了就演得正規點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生在胸部纏上白布之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥君你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會抵抗穿女裝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有點吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉要是扮男生肯定很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐要是穿男裝肯定很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是穿男裝就變得跟弟弟一模一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛無視小千的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不這樣認為  佐佐沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也無視了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千  我們還是別和這種人一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知怎麼演變成結伴一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來現在意見統一了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後大家就各走各的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多直率的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然小千就是喜歡那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼小千喜歡的都是些奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡桃子的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是那種奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣子真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡麻衣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  真有打算好好工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝影的時候把手機關了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:04:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我接個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  有認真工作的打算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能心平氣和地聽我說完嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想做的話就辭職吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說出來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  我感覺早晚都會穿幫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交男朋友本來就不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還在攝影完後碰頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然也不是抱著種隨便的心態在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也不知道該怎樣才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就應該找朋友商量不是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這種時候就應該找朋友商量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也想告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺有點像在炫耀就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼就只告訴環
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為因為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環早在我之前就有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且安那看上去討厭男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們短暫的交情就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何了  小修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就快完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼特別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想打電話給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害  我對這方面很不擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  那個舞台劇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於反串劇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥君你來寫寫看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦  二鳥君文筆那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會編故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你擁有這方面的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  巴士來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我擁有這方面才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（反串劇）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電燈太刺眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不知道體諒下人家拍攝有多辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視上都說不在暗處是無法熟睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難受死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反串劇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反串…反串…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說突然有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的男生和女生互換了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是相反
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明決定兩人作為朋友好好相處的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有些發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一陣陣地發冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  小修也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修只是熬夜了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那稍微睡會兒晚點去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又這樣順著他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他去保健室睡不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  看你沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你遮陽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥  我會跟老師請假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就乖乖躺著休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  二鳥君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有些不舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有些不舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨練時有人扭傷腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在網球場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網球場是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帶我去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…二鳥君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要穿胸罩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸罩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問了個怪問題  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想穿胸罩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥君那樣平平的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也羨慕高槻同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…關於反串劇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你決定寫了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的大致構思是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫想變成男生的女生和想變成女生的男生的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趁熱打鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的話  就趕緊回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個點子很棒哦  二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥君  二鳥君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級的學長叫你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你姐姐身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想不是很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會兒我能去看她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀨谷君好像也有點感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他莫非到變聲期了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  二鳥真遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早我們也會有這一天吧  魔之變聲期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以當作練習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不知道什麼時候就發不出這樣的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦喉結突出聲音變低就晚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕緊趁現在錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是僅僅是錄聲音沒必要打扮成女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是找個藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵當然是喜歡才這麼做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子要穿哪件？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果你也不是不願意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那從我開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家的名字叫有賀麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來是二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥要入戲才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用「人家」  名字就先用你姐姐的試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家的名字是二鳥真穗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊二鳥！  好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是二鳥真穗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個傢伙到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待著別動  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四眼  開門去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是待著別動  又是去開門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  就試著演到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有賀誠的妹妹  有賀麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  這是私闖民宅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到修的裸體  居然臉紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嚇一跳是因為你居然在強脫弟弟的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有給我好好睡著  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看到奇怪的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你的橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因為發燒才變得奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天和瀨谷接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非把感冒傳給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想成為男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想成為女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人在某天夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秘密的地方  秘密地許下願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩變成男孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩變成女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到都有兩份完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是優秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能否作為參考  互相讀讀看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然二鳥君這種原創劇本才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉同學的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密歐和茱麗葉的現代版
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是大家耳熟能詳的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我的故事要有趣得多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  老師覺得兩部都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如把這兩部的長處組合起來寫成一個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不傷害任何一方而採用共同劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種教育方式的適用期也就僅限小學而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺是不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師大概是打算採取折中方案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想就這麼結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要弄出個精彩的劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的！  如果是我和二鳥君的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出軌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你老婆告狀哦  二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺在這裡說話不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再做奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排球和籃球部即便下雨天也不休息所以才吃虧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說千葉同學人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織說今天不參加社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像不怎麼喜歡排球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:17:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  好像沒穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺比我更合適
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不穿上試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這和說好的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過不再做奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我興奮過頭了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我很開心  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮成女孩子去碰頭  感覺太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅…羅密歐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是想成為女孩的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而茱麗葉是想成為男孩的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的構想如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須記下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我是羅密歐啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我是茱麗葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是相遇後兩人不斷地幽會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是二鳥君和高槻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個  一定很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓二鳥君演茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這能夠實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅密歐是高槻同學也行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千葉同學一起  雖說有些不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過感覺會順利進行下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為女孩的羅密歐和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為男孩的茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的胸部  根本不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸罩印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  高槻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨練遲到了  我先去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻的背後…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…也有
